Patch Set 6:

A similar validation for image properties is being attempted here https://review.openstack.org/#/c/203948/

You think we can merge these to carry out a bigger effort to do this validation for most things applicable? It looks like we are doing this on a case-by-case basis so far. Why not just fix it for all possible cases?

Patch Set 6: Code-Review-1

This should have APIImpact and DocImpact.

It's important to note that this patch changes the current v1 behavior. While I think it introduces the right behavior, lets be clear that it replaces a 500 being returned with a 400.
